text: Nicholas Andrew Langworthy (born February 27, 1981) is an American Republican politician. He has been the U.S. representative for New York's 23rd district since 2023. He was formerly the chair of the New York State Republican Committee. He was the youngest state chair in party history. ==References== ==Other websites== * Congressman Nick Langworthy official U.S. House website * Nick Langworthy for Congress * Category:1981 births Category:Living people Category:United States representatives from New York (state) Category:People from Jamestown, New York Category:Republican Party (United States) politicians
